    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> sacrum </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> pro salute <expan><abbr>Imperato</abbr><ex>ris</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Oppius Maximus et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Oppius <lb n="2"/>Ianuarius sacerdotes Matris <lb n="3"/>Deum et Liberi Patris vexillo <lb n="4"/>Novesium Oppianorum <lb n="5"/>aram de suo posuerunt
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 1 u. 2 beinden sich auf der corona. Datierungsvorschlag nach Tsarov: 202 n. Chr. anläßlich des Besuchs von Nicopolis ad Istrum durch Septimius Severus.</p>
            </div>
